// 用户标准测试用例 - 针对 azimuth 库的核心功能进行测试
// 使用标准的 MoonBit 测试语法，包含 10 个测试用例

test "add_function_basic_cases" {
  // 测试加法函数的基本情况
  @azimuth.assert_eq(5, @azimuth.add(2, 3))
  @azimuth.assert_eq(0, @azimuth.add(0, 0))
  @azimuth.assert_eq(-1, @azimuth.add(-2, 1))
  @azimuth.assert_eq(100, @azimuth.add(50, 50))
}

test "multiply_function_basic_cases" {
  // 测试乘法函数的基本情况
  @azimuth.assert_eq(6, @azimuth.multiply(2, 3))
  @azimuth.assert_eq(0, @azimuth.multiply(5, 0))
  @azimuth.assert_eq(-8, @azimuth.multiply(-2, 4))
  @azimuth.assert_eq(25, @azimuth.multiply(5, 5))
}

test "greet_function_standard_cases" {
  // 测试问候函数的标准情况
  @azimuth.assert_eq_string("Hello, MoonBit!", @azimuth.greet("MoonBit"))
  @azimuth.assert_eq_string("Hello, 用户!", @azimuth.greet("用户"))
  @azimuth.assert_eq_string("Hello, !", @azimuth.greet(""))
  @azimuth.assert_eq_string("Hello, 123!", @azimuth.greet("123"))
}

test "divide_with_ceil_positive_cases" {
  // 测试向上取整除法的正数情况
  @azimuth.assert_eq(4, @azimuth.divide_with_ceil(10, 3))
  @azimuth.assert_eq(3, @azimuth.divide_with_ceil(9, 3))
  @azimuth.assert_eq(1, @azimuth.divide_with_ceil(5, 5))
  @azimuth.assert_eq(2, @azimuth.divide_with_ceil(3, 2))
}

test "divide_with_ceil_edge_cases" {
  // 测试向上取整除法的边界情况
  @azimuth.assert_eq(0, @azimuth.divide_with_ceil(5, 0))
  @azimuth.assert_eq(0, @azimuth.divide_with_ceil(0, 5))
  @azimuth.assert_eq(1, @azimuth.divide_with_ceil(1, 1))
  @azimuth.assert_eq(1, @azimuth.divide_with_ceil(99, 100))
}

test "mathematical_commutative_property" {
  // 测试数学交换律
  let a = 7
  let b = 13
  @azimuth.assert_eq(@azimuth.add(a, b), @azimuth.add(b, a))
  @azimuth.assert_eq(@azimuth.multiply(a, b), @azimuth.multiply(b, a))
}

test "zero_element_properties" {
  // 测试零元素性质
  @azimuth.assert_eq(5, @azimuth.add(5, 0))
  @azimuth.assert_eq(0, @azimuth.multiply(5, 0))
  @azimuth.assert_eq(0, @azimuth.multiply(0, 5))
  @azimuth.assert_eq(0, @azimuth.add(0, 0))
}

test "negative_number_operations" {
  // 测试负数运算
  @azimuth.assert_eq(-5, @azimuth.add(-2, -3))
  @azimuth.assert_eq(1, @azimuth.add(-3, 4))
  @azimuth.assert_eq(6, @azimuth.multiply(-2, -3))
  @azimuth.assert_eq(-6, @azimuth.multiply(2, -3))
}

test "combined_arithmetic_operations" {
  // 测试组合算术运算
  let result1 = @azimuth.add(@azimuth.multiply(2, 3), @azimuth.multiply(4, 5))
  @azimuth.assert_eq(26, result1)  // 2*3 + 4*5 = 6 + 20 = 26
  
  let result2 = @azimuth.multiply(@azimuth.add(5, 3), 2)
  @azimuth.assert_eq(16, result2)  // (5 + 3) * 2 = 8 * 2 = 16
}

test "practical_business_calculation" {
  // 测试实际业务计算场景
  let unit_price = 25
  let quantity = 8
  let shipping = 15
  
  let subtotal = @azimuth.multiply(unit_price, quantity)
  let total = @azimuth.add(subtotal, shipping)
  
  @azimuth.assert_eq(200, subtotal)
  @azimuth.assert_eq(215, total)
}